<style>
  :root {
    --color-bg-primary:#F8F9FA;
    --color-bg-header:#0A4A2F;
    --color-accent:#F28C38;
    --color-accent-hover:#E07B2D;
    --color-text-primary:#1A3C34;
    --color-text-secondary:#5C6B66;
    --color-text-muted:#8A9A94;
    --color-border:#E8F0EB;
    --font-heading:"Plus Jakarta Sans",-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;
    --font-body:"Inter",-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;
    --container:1200px;
    --radius-lg:1rem;
    --radius-xl:1.5rem;
  }
  *,::before,::after { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
  html { scroll-behavior:smooth; }
  body { font-family:var(--font-body); color:var(--color-text-primary); line-height:1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; background:#fff; }
  .container { max-width:var(--container); margin:0 auto; padding:0 1.5rem; }
  .container-narrow { max-width:780px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 1.5rem; }

  .btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:.75rem 1.5rem; border:none; border-radius:999px; font-family:var(--font-heading); font-weight:700; font-size:.9rem; text-decoration:none; cursor:pointer; transition:all .2s; }
  .btn-primary { background:var(--color-accent); color:#fff; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background:var(--color-accent-hover); transform:translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-secondary { background:transparent; color:#fff; border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.4); }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color:var(--color-accent); color:var(--color-accent); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero-story { background:var(--color-bg-header); padding:5rem 0 4rem; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
  .hero-story::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(242,140,56,.08) 0%, transparent 60%); pointer-events:none; }
  .hero-story .eyebrow { display:inline-block; background:rgba(242,140,56,.15); color:var(--color-accent); border:1px solid rgba(242,140,56,.3); padding:.4rem 1rem; border-radius:999px; font-size:.75rem; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:.12em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-family:var(--font-heading); }
  .hero-story h1 { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.5rem); font-weight:800; color:#fff; line-height:1.1; margin-bottom:1.25rem; max-width:680px; letter-spacing:-.02em; }
  .hero-story h1 em { font-family:'Lora',serif; font-style:italic; font-weight:700; color:var(--color-accent); }
  .hero-story p { color:rgba(255,255,255,.7); font-size:1.05rem; line-height:1.75; max-width:580px; margin-bottom:2rem; }
  .hero-story .btn-row { display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }

  /* ── ABOUT SECTION ── */
  .section { padding:5rem 0; }
  .section-alt { background:var(--color-bg-primary); }
  .section-dark { background:var(--color-bg-header); }

  .story-body { font-size:1rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.85; }
  .story-body p { margin-bottom:1.5rem; }
  .story-body p:last-child { margin-bottom:0; }
  .story-body strong { color:var(--color-text-primary); font-weight:600; }

  .section-eyebrow { font-size:.72rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--color-accent); margin-bottom:.6rem; font-family:var(--font-heading); }
  .section-heading { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3.5vw,2.5rem); font-weight:800; color:var(--color-text-primary); line-height:1.15; letter-spacing:-.02em; margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .section-heading-white { color:#fff; }
  .section-subtext { color:var(--color-text-secondary); font-size:1rem; line-height:1.7; max-width:600px; margin-bottom:3rem; }

  /* ── STORY CALLOUT BOX ── */
  .story-callout { background:#F0F7F2; border-left:4px solid var(--color-bg-header); border-radius:0 var(--radius-lg) var(--radius-lg) 0; padding:1.5rem 2rem; margin:2.5rem 0; }
  .story-callout p { color:var(--color-text-primary); font-size:1rem; line-height:1.75; margin:0; font-style:italic; }

  /* ── WHY CARDS ── */
  .why-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:1.25rem; }
  .why-card { background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius:var(--radius-xl); padding:2rem; transition:all .3s; }
  .why-card:hover { border-color:#0A4A2F; box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(10,74,47,.1); transform:translateY(-3px); }
  .why-card .icon { width:44px; height:44px; background:#F0F7F2; border-radius:.875rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .why-card h3 { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:1rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--color-text-primary); margin-bottom:.5rem; line-height:1.3; }
  .why-card p { font-size:.875rem; color:var(--color-text-secondary); line-height:1.65; margin:0; }

  /* ── CLOSING TRUST LINE ── */
  .trust-line { text-align:center; padding:4rem 0; }
  .trust-line h2 { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.25rem); font-weight:800; color:var(--color-text-primary); max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; line-height:1.25; letter-spacing:-.02em; }

  /* ── CTA STRIP ── */
  .cta-strip { background:var(--color-bg-header); padding:5rem 0; text-align:center; }
  .cta-strip h2 { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem); font-weight:800; color:#fff; margin-bottom:.25rem; }
  .cta-strip h2 em { font-family:'Lora',serif; font-style:italic; color:var(--color-accent); display:block; }
  .cta-strip p { color:rgba(255,255,255,.65); font-size:.95rem; margin-bottom:2rem; }
  .cta-strip .btn-row { display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }

  /* ── BREADCRUMB ── */
  .breadcrumb-bar { background:#fff; border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .breadcrumb-bar .container { max-width:1100px; }
  .breadcrumb { padding:.6rem 0; font-size:.78rem; color:var(--color-text-muted); font-family:var(--font-heading); }
  .breadcrumb a { color:var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration:none; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color:var(--color-text-primary); }
  .breadcrumb span { margin:0 .4rem; }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width:1024px) { .why-grid { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); } }
  @media (max-width:768px) {
    .hero-story { padding:3rem 0 2.5rem; }
    .why-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .section { padding:3rem 0; }
  }
  @media (max-width:480px) {
    .hero-story .btn-row { flex-direction:column; }
    .cta-strip .btn-row { flex-direction:column; align-items:center; }
  }
</style>

<!-- Breadcrumb -->
<div class="breadcrumb-bar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a><span>›</span>
      <span style="color:var(--color-text-primary);font-weight:600;">Our Story</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero-story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Our Story</div>
    <h1>Built on over 50 years of <em>family experience</em> in fresh produce</h1>
    <p>From orchard operations in Harcourt, Victoria, to wholesale supply into major fresh produce markets across Australia and direct retail through our well-known Apple of the Valley store, GrowDirect is built on real industry knowledge.</p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#about-growdirect">Read Our Story</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/collections/saver-boxes">Shop Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- About GrowDirect -->
<section class="section" id="about-growdirect">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">About GrowDirect</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">About GrowDirect</h2>

    <div class="story-body">
      <p>GrowDirect is built on over 50 years of family experience across produce growing, grading, packing, wholesale supply, and direct food retail.</p>

      <p>Our story is grounded in generations of hands-on involvement in the fresh produce industry. Over the years, our family has worked across orchard operations, fruit washing and grading, packing produce for sale, wholesale supply into major fresh produce markets across Australia, and direct-to-customer retail. That experience has given us a practical understanding of food, quality, and how produce moves from source to household.</p>

      <p>In Harcourt, Victoria, we operated an apple orchard and fruit processing facility where fruit was washed, graded by size and quality, and prepared for packing. We also owned and operated <strong>Apple of the Valley</strong>, a well-known roadside store that became a trusted stop for customers travelling from across Victoria, South Australia and New South Wales.</p>

      <div class="story-callout">
        <p>Customers visited for the freshest apples, seasonal fruit and vegetables, 100% pure honey, traditional lollies for the kids, and practical everyday value. Many still remember the small touches that made Apple of the Valley special — like receiving a complimentary takeaway coffee before heading off on the final 30 minutes to an hour of the trip home.</p>
      </div>

      <p>Quality fruit was packed for retail sale, while second-grade fruit was packed into 10kg boxes, giving families an affordable option without compromising on freshness. It was more than just a store stop; it reflected the kind of business we believed in then, and still believe in now: <strong>quality food, honest value, and genuine customer care.</strong></p>

      <p>Our involvement in wholesale supply to major fresh produce markets across Australia gave us a broader understanding of the industry — from product standards and packing requirements to market expectations, product movement, and the realities of supplying fresh food at scale.</p>

      <p><strong>GrowDirect is the modern evolution of that experience.</strong></p>

      <p>We created GrowDirect to bring together direct sourcing, practical value, and a simpler way for households to buy fresh produce and everyday food essentials. Built on decades of real industry knowledge, GrowDirect combines traditional produce experience with a modern direct-to-household model designed around trust, convenience, and honest value.</p>

      <p>At its core, GrowDirect is a family business shaped by generations in the industry and built for the way modern households shop today.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Why GrowDirect -->
