      <div class="section-eyebrow">Why GrowDirect</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin:0 auto .75rem;">Why GrowDirect</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);font-size:1rem;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.7;">Built on real produce experience, shaped by generations in the industry, and designed for the way households shop today.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="why-grid">

      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-5 8-12a8 8 0 0 0-16 0c0 7 8 12 8 12z"/><path d="M12 10a2 2 0 1 0 0-4 2 2 0 0 0 0 4z"/><path d="M12 10v5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Over 50 years of family experience</h3>
        <p>Built on generations of hands-on work across produce growing, grading, packing, wholesale supply, and direct food retail.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16Z"/><path d="m3.3 7 8.7 5 8.7-5"/><path d="M12 22V12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Real produce knowledge</h3>
        <p>Our background comes from working directly with food — understanding quality, handling, packing, and what freshness really means in practice.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Experience across the full supply chain</h3>
        <p>From orchard operations to wholesale market supply and direct household sales, we understand how food moves and what customers value.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
